title: New Comics Week 12-24-08 pt 2
description:
Here's another batch of 0-day books along with a couple of fixed files from the pt 1 torrent.

This torrent includes a fixed copy of Runaways v3 #5 and a full copy of The Astounding Wolfman #11 instead of the four page file that ended up in the pt1 torrent.

Again, Merry Christmas!

Thanks to the scanners and the original sources.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
